15:16.516 --> 15:18.618 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN, PBS NEWSHOUR:
For the past
five years, the government has
reported just

15:18.651 --> 15:23.689 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
