15:52.118 --> 15:54.687 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
But he said mining was in his
blood.

15:54.720 --> 15:56.489 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
(BEGIN VIDEO CLIP)

15:56.522 --> 16:01.994 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MACKIE BRANHAM, DIAGNOSED WITH
