17:18.437 --> 17:19.405 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
of Appalachia.

17:19.438 --> 17:21.173 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
SREENIVASAN: All right.

17:21.207 --> 17:25.378 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Let's talk about the gap between
the numbers
here, the numbers the government
documented

17:25.411 --> 17:29.482 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
and the numbers you're able to
uncover in
your investigation.

17:29.515 --> 17:31.050 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
