have black lung.

18:42.688 --> 18:47.059 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And mining -- the last mining
company you
worked for is the mining company
that saddled

18:47.093 --> 18:50.730 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
