favoring natural
gas now?

20:16.582 --> 20:21.587 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
BERKES: Well, it's also very
large coal companies
going bankrupt.

20:21.620 --> 20:29.595 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
If the coal company is
self-insured and they
don't have enough assets, then
they're not

20:29.628 --> 20:33.899 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
