23:36.849 --> 23:38.651 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
FRANCO PAVONCELLO, JOHN CABOT
UNIVERSITY IN
ROME: The Five Star Movement is
basically

23:38.684 --> 23:44.390 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
