items agents deemed
unfit to fly.

51:18.175 --> 51:21.578 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The "NewsHour'’s" Julia Griffin
met the man
behind the account.

51:21.612 --> 51:23.414 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
(BEGIN VIDEOTAPE)

51:23.447 --> 51:27.885 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JULIA GRIFFIN, PBS NEWSHOUR
CORRESPONDENT:
Guns, knives, and holiday pies,
when it comes

51:27.918 --> 51:32.589 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
