feed.

51:35.793 --> 51:42.766 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
A click-bait worthy mix of
confiscated security
items and explosive-detecting
dogs, TSA'’s

51:42.800 --> 51:47.805 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Instagram has been rated by
"Rolling Stone"
magazine as the app's fourth
best -- right

51:47.838 --> 51:49.940 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
