Beyonce.

51:49.974 --> 51:52.743 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BOB BURNS, LEAD SOCIAL MEDIA
SPECIALIST, TSA:
As a former musician, I always
wanted to make

51:52.776 --> 51:56.080 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
"Rolling Stone," and I never
imagined that
I would make it through social
media with

51:56.113 --> 51:57.081 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
TSA.

51:57.114 --> 51:59.283 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
GRIFFIN: Bob Burns runs the
agency's feed.

51:59.316 --> 52:03.520 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BURNS: I think they find it
