the knives
and grenades.

52:06.590 --> 52:12.296 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GRIFFIN: Some of the bizarre
highlights include:
a homemade avalanche charger,
this bag of

52:12.329 --> 52:19.203 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
