in a clay
souvenir pot, and, of course,
canines at work

52:19.236 --> 52:20.204 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
and at play.

52:20.237 --> 52:22.539 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
BURNS: You can never go wrong
with the dogs.

52:22.573 --> 52:24.708 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
GRIFFIN: But the most-liked
post?

52:24.742 --> 52:29.079 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
This full-sized dummy corpse
from the film
"The Texas Chainsaw Massacre."

52:29.113 --> 52:32.649 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BURNS: I don't know how they
