check incident reports.

52:38.589 --> 52:44.628 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And while the stream of
explosives and weapons
might trigger alarm, Burns
contends it shows

52:44.661 --> 52:47.998 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
