getting the
job done.

52:48.032 --> 52:49.900 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
BURNS: I think it acts as a
deterrent.

52:49.933 --> 52:53.070 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It shows that we're finding
these things,
and if anyone was thinking about
sneaking

52:53.103 --> 52:56.073 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
